headline: State Street to Speak at the Barclays Global Financial Services Conference
summary: BOSTON, August 28, 2025--State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT) announced today that its Chief Financial Officer, John Woods, and President of Investment Services, Joerg Ambrosius, will present at the Barclays 23rd Annual Global Financial Services Conference in New York, NY on Wednesday, September 10, 2025 at approximately 10:30 am ET.
